{"tid":909842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同學炮製「加料」飯盒？ 國際學校中一生肚痛送院","createTime":"2018-11-20T16:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T22:59:41.000Z","uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d15b59bffd9de370db3585ea8afcd784a7e2a101","tid":909842,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:45:40.000Z","msg":"【21:50】事主為荔枝角一間國際學校的中一生<br />\n<br />\n中學生疑遭同學整蠱，飯盒被「加料」！荔枝角一間國際學校一名12歲姓黃的中一男生，下午進食飯盒期間，發現有苦味，未幾即感到肚痛，校方通知其家長。至下午2時許，黃母將兒子帶往九龍城聖德肋撒醫院求診，醫護人員通知警方。警員接報到場，將男童轉往伊利沙伯醫院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，校方指，有同學聲稱較早時看見有人將消毒酒精加入黃童的飯盒內。警方刑事調查隊正接手跟進。"},{"pid":"68b347f9d78c02d58288db5675075ab9c259544a","tid":909842,"uid":173480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef2773c1c65f043cdc70291fadda98e47976db1","tid":909842,"uid":191815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T17:28:31.000Z","msg":"謀殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f270742fc6cc62ccffd7f21707a6411dbeed0ae","tid":909842,"uid":46862,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T17:31:17.000Z","msg":"cais?"},{"pid":"bf085606616b778b0e5299fe03bee1a0649ad3bf","tid":909842,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T18:05:17.000Z","msg":"地利亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43610729cdbfa8d6331d5c96f704292d51b445e1","tid":909842,"uid":82542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T18:14:11.000Z","msg":"rich 去私家醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb0337c68faf8ef29efaab09a16f0ecb9e670f1","tid":909842,"uid":66943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T20:19:29.000Z","msg":"加CH3OH<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04704e03fbd879170dfedeab7de8306251be1dc","ti